name: Ghostie Eats
description:
As it is Ghostie's first appearance on Hicetnunc, it seemed fitting to show Ghostie the ghost doing what it loves most, eating tez. It may sound uncharacteristic and rather inefficient for a ghost to eat. But Ghostie isn't like all the other ghost's. It’s probably why Ghostie never gets full and is forever hungry.
